*& Data: 01/05/2022
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zclientes1700 LINE-COUNT 65.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Tables
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
TABLES kna1.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Types / Structure
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
TYPES: BEGIN OF ty_kna1,
         kunnr TYPE kna1-kunnr,
         name1 TYPE kna1-name1,
         ort01 TYPE kna1-ort01,
         regio TYPE kna1-regio,
         stras TYPE kna1-stras,
       END OF ty_kna1.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  WorkArea
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
DATA wa_kna1 TYPE ty_kna1.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Internal Table
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
DATA ti_kna1 TYPE TABLE OF ty_kna1.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Top-of-Page - Topo da página.
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
TOP-OF-PAGE.

  WRITE: 1 'Codigo',
         12 'Nome',
         48 'Cidade',
         84 'UF'.
  ULINE.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Selection Screen
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
  SELECT-OPTIONS s_kunnr FOR kna1-kunnr.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Start-Of-Selection - Evento
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
START-OF-SELECTION.
* Open SQL ( Selecionando Dados )
  SELECT kunnr
         name1
         ort01
         regio
         stras
         FROM kna1
         INTO TABLE ti_kna1
         WHERE kunnr IN s_kunnr.

* Impressao dos dados

  LOOP AT ti_kna1 INTO wa_kna1.

    WRITE: / wa_kna1-kunnr,
             wa_kna1-name1,
             wa_kna1-ort01,
             wa_kna1-regio,
             wa_kna1-stras.

  ENDLOOP.
